snippet.title: Banana Drama | Official Trailer | Online RTS Multiplayer Game | Ver. 1.0
snippet.description:
We are currently looking for sponsors. Please write us for more information: bananadrama.game@gmail.com

Banana Drama is an online multiplayer game with currently up to 4 players per room.
Banana Drama is an early access release which means that some bugs might occur.  
Check out our official discord server: https://discord.gg/FpYd9eSfme 
We appreciate your feedback. Develop the game with us!

Developed by: 
@dommenuss (Instagram)
@bhynchau (Instagram)
@lenau_ria (Instagram)

Music by: 
Victor Cooper - Windwalker (Seven Hearts Edit) provided by Tunetank.

All rights reserved. For questions send us an e-mail or contact us on steam.
bananadrama.game@gmail.com
